Meshka',1999,'11-50 employees','MEP Contracting & Trading Company HVAC- Fire Fighting- Fire Alarm- LED light trader & agent and measurement devices for Steel factory.',NULL,'Egypt',NULL),('Alexandria Business Association- SMEs Project',1990,'More than 1000 employees','بدأت جمعية رجال أعمال أسكندرية – مشروع تنمية المنشآت الصغيرة والحرفية نشاطها فى دعم وتنمية المنشآت الصغيرة ومتناهية الصغر التى لم تكن قادرة على الحصول على قروض من خلال النظام المصرفى التقليدى فى عام 1990. و تسعى الجمعية من خلال رسالتها الى تقديم المنتجات المالية وغير المالية لتلبية احتياجات العملاء الأكثر احتياجا من الناشطين اقتصاديا وأصحاب المشروعات الناشئة لتحقيق حياة أفضل لهم ولأسرهم مع المحافظة على توازن الأداء الاقتصادى والاجتماعي . وتقدم الجمعية خدماتها فى 18 محافظة من خلال (107فرعا )','Alexandria','Egypt',NULL),('Alexandria For Programming',2008,'11-50 employees','Alexandria for programming is a mobile app development company located in Alexandria- it was established in 2008- and we have 14+ years of experience. You can see our introduction video here : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NwtAw0jyc6M&t=3s','Alexandria','Egypt',NULL),('alfanar',1976,'More than 1000 employees','alfanar is a privately owned company • Total turnover 3 B$ • Headcount 20-000+ employees • Significant growth: +20 % on average since 2009 • Profitable company • Quality is our competitive advantage • People are no. 1 asset','Cairo','Egypt',NULL),('Algoriza',2011,'51-100 employees','Algoriza is a leading software house specialized in Software Development and Information Technology Services. What we do? We run four business lines: - Web and Mobile development - Hybrid Offshore Delivery Model - Artificial Intelligence - Digital Marketing. Our philosophy is to deliver the products in an effective and efficient manner at very competitive rate. Our teams are working to serve different regions such as United Arab Emirates- Saudi Arabia and Egypt with a deep experience to ensure our products and services are in line with global best practices and achieve enduring business outcomes.','Giza','Egypt',NULL),('Ali Alkhajeh Development',2022,'51-100 employees','AA Development is a groundbreaking real estate company led by Emirati investor Ali Al Khajeh. With a commitment to innovation- we create extraordinary properties. Connect with us on LinkedIn for updates and opportunities.','Cairo','Egypt',NULL),('Aliaict',2018,'101-500 employees','ALIA ICT is one of the fastest growing professional ICT services companies in the middle east region- enables the successful digital transformation of business and operating models by utilizing disruptive technologies to create new customer experiences- achieve cost efficiencies- and gain competitive advantage with speed and agility. Our unique industry-based- consultative approach helps clients envision- build and run more innovative and efficient businesses. Headquartered in Riyadh- Saudi Arabia. We have our offices in India- Jordan and Egypt with a team of highly skilled multinational resources combines positive attitude- passion for client satisfaction- innovation- deep industry and business process knowledge and altogether helping ALIA in connecting the ICT dots to build a better future for our prestigious clients. What makes us unique is our ability to help clients meet both challenges. We help them enhance productivity by ensuring that vital business functions work faster- cheaper and better. And- our ability to conceptualize- architect and implement new and expanded capabilities allows transformative changes to take clients business to the next level.','Cairo','Egypt',NULL),('Alkarma Developments',1995,'51-100 employees','At Al Karma Developments- we are industry pioneers in real estate development on the west side of Cairo. Since the beginning in 1996- we have been adeptly designing state-of-the-art residential compounds while striving to deliver top-notch quality. Throughout the 2000’s- Alkarma has been tirelessly perfecting the art of developing projects. F